title: LORD OF THE JUNGLE 011-013 (2013) (Digital) (Fawkes-Empire)
description: The original Lord of the Jungle has returned! If you thought you knew the story, think again! For the first time in its 100-year history the classic Edgar Rice Burroughs story, Tarzan of The Apes, is being told - UNCENSORED! This Dynamite series captures the savagery and action of the original while expanding on it with new elements! Written by Arvid Nelson and illustrated by Roberto Castro.
